  "detailed_description": "*****Before purchasing: This game only contains one mini-game (2D side-scrolling gameplay), which lasts approximately 2 to 5 hours (depending on whether you pursue collectibles). It is not a fully-fledged game in the traditional sense; rather, it's the first part of a series of \"components\" designed to fundraise (for developing my 3A). Its non-essential features (such as options settings, UI, and almost everything outside of the mini-game world) are of low completion. I strongly recommend anyone to watch its trailer before purchasing*****<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhile I'm still young, I just want to give it a try, even if it might cost me the rest of my life.",
